latestPosts.caption:
One pair of pants, for LITERALLY all your plans — they’re ‘Her All Day’ Pants by @pepr_official 🤌🏼

Save this for when you’re hunting for a wear-everywhere essential 🩶 

#PEPR #HerAllDayPants

If you ask me my fav Sunday outfit? It’s got to be this — a dreamy kaftan (from @petalsfromhergarden) that feels like a warm hug and looks like slow living 🤎🌸

From the earthy rust bottom to the hand-blocked blush top, it’s all in the details — relaxed, flowy, and styled with just enough to match the mellow light ☀️ 

ANDDD got the calming Sunday energy going for me in this chaotic city 🤍

Jewellery by @sachdeva.ritika ✨
Save for when you’re looking to dress to slow down 😌

Some Sunday fun with my peeeps @keegancrasto @publicbutterindia @makeupbyhabiba2024 📸🫶🖌️

#PetalsFromHerGarden #StyleMeetsSlowDays #StyledbyAnshika
